oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bar-N Ranch - Unknown date - Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WLS Bar-N Ranch radio program, unknown broadcast date, part 2. Cast includes Red Foley, Aunt Sally Newcombe, Salty Holmes, Judy Martin, and the Boys From The Bunkhouse (including Russ, Ernie, and Charlie on fiddle), with announcer Jack Mitchell. Circa mid-1940s based on performances.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Red Foley; Boys From The Bunkhouse; Aunt Sally Newcombe; Salty Holmes; Judy Martin
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Comedy routine (Red Foley, Aunt Sally Newcombe, Salty Holmes, Judy Martin, Ernie) -- Aunt Sally Newcombe introduces Salty Holmes -- Mama Blues (Salty Holmes harmonica) -- Red Foley and Aunt Sally introduce Judy Martin -- Silver Dew On The Bluegrass Tonight (Judy Martin) -- Comedy routine (Salty Holmes, Red Foley, Judy Martin) -- Sky Ball Paint (Red Foley) -- Aunt Sally Newcombe and Red Foley talk -- Old Dog Tray (Red Foley) -- Red Foley talks -- Cindy (Red Foley, cast) -- Closing statement (Aunt Sally Newcombe, Red Foley) -- Theme (Cimarron (Roll On)) -- Closing statement (Jack Mitchell)
